{
  "stem": "25639.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The streets were all closed form the rubble, as the houses fell onto the streets sometimes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to, of course, clear this, and push it over to the sidewalk, and then from the sidewalk over to the building, as we did in Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the same purpose.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And again, I was there for a limited period of time, maybe about three weeks or four weeks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I really can't recall accurately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we were shipped out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from there, I was sent to a little town called Beendorf.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's B-E-E-N-D-O-R-F.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, it was only something like population 800, a very small town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was a very significant place for-- in Germany, for in the-- in a salt mine, which was so huge that it really ran clear across the town and beyond on both ends.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As I researched, I saw on the map that-- how big it is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a huge salt mountain, white.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it would shine as we would walk to work toward dusk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we'd work during the night and-- we had the night shift-- and come back at about sunrise, to our barrack.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, I worked 1,200 feet underground in a gallery.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were a series of galleries.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the way-- the place looked like an anthill, an enlarged anthill underground.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Everything was white.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and the streets were narrow, of course, and just long enough for maybe a-- I don't know-- maybe 5 and 1/2 feet or a 6 feet tall person to go by without bending over.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- we-- a huge elevator took us down into the mine shaft.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from there, we walked into the gallery that was filled with machines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That-- everything was white.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
